sequenceDiagram
  actor User
  participant FE as Frontend
  participant API as FastAPI
  participant RAG as InterviewRagService
  participant DB as MongoDB

  User->>FE: Upload resume (PDF)
  FE->>API: POST /upload-resume
  API->>RAG: interview_rag_pipeline(resume)
  RAG-->>API: questions, skills
  API->>DB: save user session
  DB-->>API: session_id
  API-->>FE: questions + topics
  FE-->>User: Show topics & questions
